<style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap');
      .main-set-up-section .container{max-width:1446px;margin:0 auto;}
    .set-up-wrap {
        display: flex;
      margin:52px 0 84px;
          column-gap: 30px;
          align-items: center;
    }
    .set-up-wrap .left-s-content{text-align:center;}
    .set-up-wrap .left-s-content h1{font-size:31px;color:#707070;line-height:normal;font-weight:500;    font-family: "Montserrat";    margin-bottom: 20px;}
     .set-up-wrap .left-s-content p{font-size:18px;line-height:27px;color:#000;font-family: "Montserrat";    max-width: 657px;
      margin: 0 auto;}
      .set-up-wrap .left-s-content,.set-up-wrap .right-s-video{width:50%;}
    .set-up-wrap .right-s-video{height:398px;}
    .set-up-wrap .right-s-video iframe{width:100%;height:100%;border-width:0}
    .bottom-set-content h2{font-size:21px;line-height:normal;color:#707070;font-weight:500;padding:10px 0;}
    .bottom-set-content p,.bottom-set-content ul li{font-size:16px;line-height:24px;color:#000;font-weight:400;font-family: "Montserrat";}
    .bottom-set-content ul{list-style-type:decimal;padding-left:21px;margin-top:30px;}
      .bottom-set-content .bottom-set-inner{max-width:792px;}
    .set-help-btn{text-align:center;max-width:153px;margin:0 auto;    padding: 40px 0 30px;}
    .set-help-btn a{display: block;
      padding: 10px 18px;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 23px;
      font-size: 19px;
      line-height: 29px;
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 700;
      background-color: #97ca3b;
      text-decoration: none; font-family: "Montserrat";font-weight:400;max-width:153px;}
    @media only screen and (max-width: 1500px) {
      .main-set-up-section .container{padding:0 8%;}
    }
      @media only screen and (max-width: 767px) {
         .main-set-up-section .container{padding:0 5%;}
        .set-up-wrap{    flex-direction: column;
      row-gap: 10px;    margin: 52px 0 39px;}
        .set-up-wrap .right-s-video {
      height: 100%;
  }
        .set-up-wrap .left-s-content, .set-up-wrap .right-s-video{width:100%;}
      }
</style>
<div class="main-set-up-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="set-up-wrap">
      <div class="left-s-content">
        <h1>Ready for silent nights?</h1>
        <p>Follow along and set up your device. For other questions visit the Help Center.</p>
        <p>
          Remember to give yourself 7 nights to get used to the movement of your pillow. Smart Nora will fade into the
          background over time.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="right-s-video">
        <iframe
          src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/511226720?autoplay=0&amp;loop=0"
          title="Embedded Vimeo Video"
          allowfullscreen=""
        >
        </iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="bottom-set-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="bottom-set-inner">
        <h2>Does your Pebble have a purple flashing light?</h2>
        <p>To pair the Pebble and Base:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Connect</strong> Pebble and Base with USB cable. Both the Pebble and the Base should be OFF.</li>
          <li><strong>Turn ON</strong> the Base.</li>
          <li><strong>Unlock</strong> the Pebble.</li>
          <li>
            On the Pebble, <strong>Press and Hold</strong> the Bluetooth Button for 3 seconds. A purple light will
            flash, then stop flashing when Bluetooth connection is established.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          <strong>If the purple light keeps flashing</strong> for more than 10 seconds, press the ON button to stop the
          flashing and press ON again to turn on the Pebble.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>If the purple light stops flashing,</strong> turn the Pebble ON. The LED should show a solid white
          light. Nora is now ready.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="set-help-btn">
    <a target="_blank" href="https://support.smartnora.com/">Help Center </a>
  </div>
</div>

